{"tid":2090824,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"Judge: HK Police is contradictory, exaggerated, dishonest","createTime":"2020-07-02T10:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T10:56:28.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c216291ac6fae774167dadab8e2ec34880bfb167","tid":2090824,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:56:28.000Z","msg":"17歲男學生被指去年7月在天水圍用雨傘襲擊休班警長。案件於屯門裁判法院經審訊後，裁判官葉啓亮今裁定被告普通襲擊罪名不成立，直指警長證供矛盾及誇大，令人難以接受，其庭上說法、書面供詞與案發影片嚴重不一致，使案情出現三個版本。辯方指警長涉作假證供，問法庭會否轉介案件到律政司跟進，惟葉官稱由「警方自己考慮」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200702/AVY7ILSBT7LOSPBR42TO5DER24/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200702%2FAVY7ILSBT7LOSPBR42TO5DER24%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8BZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=c2e382dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200702%2FAVY7ILSBT7LOSPBR42TO5DER24%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=2b01382a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200702/AVY7ILSBT7LOSPBR42TO5DER24/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"}]}